item.title: I need someone who can help me fix 667 client
item.dc:creator: @alex321 alex321
item.description:
@alex321 wrote:

[quote=“skiller8860, post:2, topic:435598”]Yes, I do know what you’re feeling bro… I got 32 errors at the moment now… It’s just the fact that the entire client is fucked up… :/.

Here’s the Compiler code that I use that brings the errors down, figure the rest out on your own… as that’s what i’m doing :L… I posted a topic, but rarely anyone knows it… so I guess i’m on my own… well you and I both :/. Anyhow, here’s the compiler code that brings the errors down just a bit:

@echo off "C:/Program Files/java/jdk1.7.0_03/bin/javac" -classpath bin -cp lib/libs.jar:lib/graphics.jar src/*.java src/jaclib/peer/*.java src/jaclib/hardware_info/*.java src/jaclib/memory/*.java src/jaclib/memory/heap/*.java src/jagdx/*.java src/jagex3/graphics2/hw/*.java src/jagex3/jagmisc/*.java src/jaggl/*.java src/jagtheora/misc/*.java src/jagtheora/ogg/*.java src/jagtheora/theora/*.java src/jagtheora/vorbis/*.java pause[/quote]
Thank you i will try
